## 8. REST API Reference

**Base URL:** `http://localhost:3000/api`

### Admin Endpoints (require `x-api-key` header)

| Method | Endpoint | Body | Description |
|--------|----------|------|-------------|
| `POST` | `/admin/constituency` | `{ constituencyID, stateID }` | Create new constituency |
| `POST` | `/admin/constituency/:id/start` | — | Start election (VOTING phase) |
| `POST` | `/admin/constituency/:id/end` | — | End election (CLOSED phase) |
| `POST` | `/admin/candidate` | `{ candidateID, name, party, constituencyID }` | Register candidate |
| `POST` | `/voter/register` | `{ epicNumber, constituencyID, stateID }` | Register voter |
| `GET`  | `/voter/history/:epicNumber` | — | Voter audit trail |
| `GET`  | `/audit/voter/:epicNumber` | — | Full on-chain voter history |
| `GET`  | `/audit/votes/:constituencyID` | — | All votes in constituency |

### Public Endpoints (no authentication)

| Method | Endpoint | Description |
|--------|----------|-------------|
| `POST` | `/voter/vote` | Cast a vote (`{ epicNumber, candidateID }`) |
| `GET`  | `/results/:constituencyID` | Live results (candidates + vote counts) |
| `GET`  | `/results/constituency/:id` | Constituency status & phase |
| `GET`  | `/results/:constituencyID/votes` | All vote transaction records |
| `GET`  | `/health` | Backend health check |

### Error Codes

| HTTP Code | Meaning | When |
|-----------|---------|------|
| 401 | Unauthorized | Missing `x-api-key` header on admin route |
| 403 | Forbidden | Invalid API key or cross-constituency vote |
| 409 | Conflict | Duplicate entity or duplicate vote |
| 423 | Locked | Election not in VOTING phase |
| 404 | Not Found | Constituency/voter not found |

